  "subject": "Replace gmaven-plugin with gmavenplus-plugin for Java 17",
  "commit_message": "Replace gmaven-plugin with gmavenplus-plugin for Java 17\n\nThe gmaven-plugin:1.0 fails on Java 17 with:\nInaccessibleObjectException: Unable to make\njava.lang.String(char[],int,int,java.lang.Void)\naccessible: module java.base does not opens java.lang\n\nReplace with gmavenplus-plugin:3.0.2 + Groovy 4.0.15\nwhich is compatible with Java 17's module system.\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4145\nChange-Id: Ie1777778f947adcbe2e80c7113ac4819dc7078ab\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
